<summary>Chatterino is a chat client for Twitch.tv</summary>
<releaseNotes>
### 2.3.1
- Major: Fixed crashing with the extension
- Major: Added the ability to highlight messages based on user badges.
- Minor: Added search filters to find messages of specific types.
- Minor: Added a setting to hide Twitch Predictions badges.
- Minor: Added image links to the badge context menu.
- Minor: Added the option to remove spaces between emotes.
- Minor: Added visual indicator to message length if over 500 characters long.
- Minor: Improved UX of `Rename Tab` dialog.
- Bugfix: Handle new user messages ("rituals") properly.
- Bugfix: Clicking on split header focuses its split.
- Bugfix: Fixed visual glitch with smooth scrolling.
- Bugfix: Added missing Copy/Open link context menu entries to emotes in Emote Picker.
</releaseNotes>
